column5: (ID Units:  SF: ) Uniquely identifies this as a SunSpec Inverter  Modbus Map; 101: single phase, 102: split phase, 103: three phase - Range: 101, 102, 103
(L Units: Registers SF: ) Length of inverter model block - Range: 50
(A Units: A SF: A_SF) AC Total Current value - Range:
(AphA Units: A SF: A_SF) AC Phase-A Current value - Range:
(AphB Units: A SF: A_SF) AC Phase-B Current value - Range:
(AphC Units: A SF: A_SF) AC Phase-C Current value - Range:
(A_SF Units:  SF: ) AC Current Scale factor - Range:
(PPVphAB Units: V SF: V_SF) AC Voltage Phase-AB value - Range:
(PPVphBC Units: V SF: V_SF) AC Voltage Phase-BC value - Range:
(PPVphCA Units: V SF: V_SF) AC Voltage Phase-CA value - Range:
(PhVphA Units: V SF: V_SF) AC Voltage Phase-A-to-neutral value - Range:
(PhVphB Units: V SF: V_SF) AC Voltage Phase-B-to-neutral value - Range:
(PhVphC Units: V SF: V_SF) AC Voltage Phase-C-to-neutral value - Range:
(V_SF Units:  SF: ) AC Voltage Scale factor - Range:
(W Units: W SF: W_SF) AC Power value - Range:
(W_SF Units:  SF: ) AC Power Scale factor - Range:
(Hz Units: Hz SF: Hz_SF) AC Frequency value - Range:
(Hz_SF Units:  SF: ) Scale factor - Range:
(VA Units: VA SF: VA_SF) Apparent Power - Range:
(VA_SF Units:  SF: ) Scale factor - Range:
(VAr Units: VAr SF: VAr_SF) Reactive Power - Range:
(VAr_SF Units:  SF: ) Scale factor - Range:
(PF Units: % SF: PF_SF) Power Factor - Range:
(PF_SF Units:  SF: ) Scale factor - Range:
(WH Units: Wh SF: WH_SF) AC Lifetime Energy production - Range:
(WH_SF Units:  SF: ) AC Lifetime Energy production scale factor - Range:
(DCA Units: A SF: DCA_SF) DC Current value - Range: Not supported if multiple DC inputs; current can be found in Multiple MPPT model
(DCA_SF Units:  SF: ) Scale factor - Range: Not supported if multiple DC inputs.
(DCV Units: V SF: DCV_SF) DC Voltage value - Range: Not supported if multiple DC inputs; voltage can be found in Multiple MPPT model
(DCV_SF Units:  SF: ) Scale factor - Range: Not supported if multiple DC inputs.
(DCW Units: W SF: DCW_SF) DC Power value - Range: Total power of all DC inputs
(DCW_SF Units:  SF: ) Scale factor - Range:
(TmpCab Units: 째 C SF: Tmp_SF) Cabinet Temperature - Range: Not supported
(TmpSnk Units: 째 C SF: Tmp_SF) Coolant or Heat Sink Temperature - Range: Not supported
(TmpTrns Units: 째 C SF: Tmp_SF) Transformer Temperature - Range: Not supported
(TmpOt Units: 째 C SF: Tmp_SF) Other Temperature - Range: Not supported
(Tmp_SF Units:  SF: ) Scale factor - Range: Not supported
(St Units: Enumerated SF: N/A) Operating State - Range:
(StVnd Units: Enumerated SF: N/A) Vendor Defined Operating State - Range:
(Evt1 Units: Bitfield SF: N/A) Event Flags (bits 0-31) - Range:
(Evt2 Units: Bitfield SF: N/A) Event Flags (bits 32-63) - Range:
(EvtVnd1 Units: Bitfield SF: N/A) Vendor Defined Event Flags (bits 0-31) - Range:
(EvtVnd2 Units: Bitfield SF: N/A) Vendor Defined Event Flags (bits 32-63) - Range:
(EvtVnd3 Units: Bitfield SF: N/A) Vendor Defined Event Flags (bits 64-95) - Range:
(EvtVnd4 Units: Bitfield SF: N/A) Vendor Defined Event Flags (bits 96-127) - Range:
